  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You expend some of your rage to strike your opponents with a more powerful weapon blow.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Str 13, rage class feature, Power Attack, base attack bonus +12.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While raging and using Power Attack, you can spend 3 additional rounds of your rage as a swift action to add your Constitution bonus on damage rolls for melee attacks or thrown weapon attacks you make on your turn. If you are using the weapon two-handed, instead add 1-1/2 times your Constitution bonus. This bonus damage is not multiplied on a critical hit. ",
